  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The event-related potentials may be different in patients with Takotsubo cardiomyopathy than
      in patients without Takotsubo.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In patients with Takotsubo diagnosed by coronary angiography, the event-related potentials
      are investigated and compared with a control group, which consists of subjects without
      Takotsubo.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
